      "text": "えへへー\n{user}さんとプチデート！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh hehe.\n{user}-san‚ it's like a mini date!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "こらこら。二人で海辺を歩いてるだけだろ？　はぁ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We're just walking by the beach okay? …Sigh.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 17.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_03-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "あー。{user}さん、今\n「あれ、なんだかカップルみたいだな」って思った？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah! {user}-san‚ just now… Did you just think‚\n\"Hmm‚ we really look like a couple tho\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "……いや、別に思ってないぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…No‚ I didn't think that at all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 27.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_03-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "ふふふ、そういうことにしておいてあげましょう\nふんふんふ～ん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehehe‚ let's just say you did.\nHumming~ Humming~…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.9,
      "sfxList": [
