      "text": "ぜぇ、ぜぇ、ぜぇ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "*PANTING*",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_03-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、大丈夫？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ are you okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "な、なんとかな……。お返ししようにも、全く\n追いつけなかった……。ここまで体力に差があるとは",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-Yeah… Even if I wanted to get back at you‚ I couldn't catch up.\nThe difference in stamina is surprising… I guess it's the result of…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 68.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_03-mei008.m4a",
      "text": "日々の積み重ねってやつかなー\n月ストのみんなといっぱい練習してるからね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Maybe it's the accumulation of daily efforts.\nI've been practicing a lot with the Moon Tempest…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.9343333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_03-mei009.m4a",
      "text": "あ、そういえば……ライブ前に\n琴乃ちゃんと渚ちゃんが海の家に来たよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ by the way… Before the live‚\nKotono-chan and Nagisa-chan came to the beach restaurant.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 83.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_03-mei010.m4a",
      "text": "二人とも、芽衣が料理を運んでるのを見て\nびっくりしてたなー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They were surprised\nto see me serving the dishes.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 89.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_03-mei011.m4a",
      "text": "渚ちゃんが琴乃ちゃんにかき氷をあーんしてて\n照れてる琴乃ちゃん、可愛かった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nagisa-chan was feeding shaved ice to Kotono-chan‚\nand Kotono-chan looked so cute being embarrassed.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "相変わらず仲がいいな\n他には誰か来たのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They still have such a good relationship.\nDid anyone else come?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 102.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_03-mei012.m4a",
      "text": "後はねー、怜ちゃんが来たよ\n呼び込みを手伝ってくれたんだけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After that‚ Rei-chan came.\nShe helped with the promotion…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 109.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_05_03-mei013.m4a",
      "text": "スーパータケミヤでバイトしてただけあって、気合いが\n違ったよ。通りがかった人がびっくりしてたもん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But her enthusiasm was different. Being a part-timer at\nthe market Takemiya really made a difference…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 117.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
